# Web Frontend Rules

- Use Redux Toolkit slices for cross-page state.
- Keep server calls in async thunks/services, not in presentational components.
- Use Tailwind utility classes only; do not introduce custom CSS files.
- Keep dark/light theme toggling consistent via app-level state.
- Build screens around domain flows: employee add, task assignment, progress updates, leave, finance.
